  <summary>&lt;p>----- The Plasma Window Decorations for Catppuccin's Mocha Modern Aurorae 6 -----&lt;br />&lt;br />Catppuccin is a community-driven pastel theme that aims to be a middle ground between low and high contrast themes. It consists of 4 soothing warm palettes with 26 eye-candy colours each, perfect for coding, designing, and much more! Here, it's used as a colourscheme for KDE Plasma. Hope you enjoy!&lt;br />&lt;br />Any issues can be reported here: &lt;a href="https://github.com/catppuccin/kde/issues">https://github.com/catppuccin/kde/issues&lt;/a>&lt;/p></summary>
